data.description: Beautiful home for sale in Fallon Nevada! The home features beautiful luxury vinyl plank flooring in all the living areas as well as the master bedroom. The two off bedrooms have brand new carpet. Along with new flooring, the entire house has new baseboards and all the doors have been freshly painted with new casings. New vanities in both bathrooms giving the house an updated move in ready feel. The living room, kitchen, and hallways have been freshly painted. This home has a large backyard with mature trees. The kitchen features a lot of counter space, with lots of cabinets that have plenty of storage. This would be a great starter home, or investment property.
